values: Since the whole "pretending to be Terri Schiavo" was done first (and better) by , and the "Terri's a retard, so I'll post random letters" was already done by Terri's blogspot blog, I'll just post about my undying love of chocolate cake with mint frosting. And sprinkles. Or maybe, I'll just post some 9/11 jokes. Q: Why didn't Superman stop the terrorists from destroying the World Trade Center? A: Because he's a quadriplegic! Q: Why are FDNY and NYPD considered some of New York's finest? A: Becasuse you can run them through a sieve! Q: How long does it take to reach the ground from 107 stories up? A: The rest of your life! Q: How many New Yorkers does it take to change a light bulb? A: God knows, they keep jumping out the window when it gets too hot! Q: What's the number one drink served on United Airlines? A: Flaming Manhattan Q: How many Americans died in the WTC yesterday? A: Who gives a fuck?
AHHHHHHH WAAAAAAAAnt you assholes to stop making my life (or lack thereof) into such a circus. Seriously!
